Package de.parsemis.parsers

Contains a huge amount of parsers for read/write graphs from/to files/data streams.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
GraphmlLabelParser<LabelType> This interface encapsulate the ability to read and write different label types
GraphParser<NodeType,EdgeType> This interface declares the functionality to parse and serialize graphs
LabelParser<LabelType> This interface encapsulates the ability to read and write different label types.
 

Class Summary
CccGraphParser<NodeType,EdgeType> This class implements a (simple and not complete) parser of the CCC-graph format This format is used by the research team of Prof Gasteiger.
DotGraphParser<NodeType,EdgeType> This class implements a (simple and not complete) parser of the Dot-file format.
GraphmlParser<NodeType,EdgeType> This class implements a (simple and not complete) parser of the Graphml-file format
IntLabelParser This class is the specialized label parser for Integers
LineGraphParser<NodeType,EdgeType> This class can parse graphs in LineGraph (.lg) format
MapLabelParser This class is a parser for multi-attributed labels stored as strings in a map
MXMLParser<NodeType,EdgeType> This class implements a (simple and not complete) parser of the mxml-file format
SimpleDirectedGraphParser<NodeType,EdgeType> This class is the parser of the simple directed graph (.sdg) format that stores the graphs as adjacent matrices
SimpleUndirectedGraphParser<NodeType,EdgeType> This class is the parser of the simple undirected graph (.sug) format that stores the graphs as symmetric adjacent matrices
SmilesParser This class is the parser of the smiles format (.smiles) that is for in chemical databases
StringLabelParser This class is the spezialized label parser for Strings
SubdueGraphParser<NodeType,EdgeType> This class implements a (simple and not complete) parser of the subdue-graph format
SubdueParser<NodeType,EdgeType> This class implements a parser for the subdue graph file format
 

Package de.parsemis.parsers Description

Contains a huge amount of parsers for read/write graphs from/to files/data streams.

These GraphParser parse/serialze one or a set of Graph objects of the de.parsemis.graph package.

Author:
Marc Woerlein (woerlein@informatik.uni-erlangen.de)
